video.title: Franny's Feet
video.synopsis: Franny Fantootsie tries on shoes brought to her grandfather's shop for repair, and each pair takes her on a magical adventure somewhere in the world.

episodes.synopsis: A little sheep is not as wooly as the other sheep/A hermit crab needs a new shell.
episodes.title: Wonderful Woolies / Home For Herman

episodes.synopsis: A fire station dog feels he's too small/A magic show rabbit is scared of the dark.
episodes.title: Small Is Beautiful / Opening Night Jitters

episodes.synopsis: A lonely abominable snowman need a friends/A native girl at a Potlach loses her dancing dress.
episodes.title: Not Yeti / Jingle Dress

episodes.synopsis: A rodeo horse isn't cut out to be a bucking bronco/A jungle monkey who's afraid to climb trees.
episodes.title: Ride 'em Cowboy / Monkey Stuff

episodes.synopsis: A rhino and his oxpecker have a spat/Twin sisters need costumes for the Chinese New Year's parade.
episodes.title: You Bug Me / Double Trouble

episodes.synopsis: A young Japanese boy finds a birthday present for his grandfather/A duck with a cold thinks it's time to fly south.
episodes.title: Paper Presents / Fowl Weather

episodes.synopsis: An ostrich tries to patch the crack in the egg it's babysitting/Two sled dogs have to learn to work together.
episodes.title: Egg Sitting / Arctic Antics

episodes.synopsis: A dawdling fish loses his school/A bear can't get to sleep (hibernate) without his stuffed toy.
episodes.title: Under The Sea / Bedtime For Bears

episodes.synopsis: A hilarious hamster tries to avoid getting a check-up/An excitable skunk learns to be a good sport.
episodes.title: Visit To The Vet / Game Over

episodes.synopsis: A library mouse and a library cat discover they have a love of reading in common/A young Jester at a Renaissance Fair can't make people laugh.
episodes.title: The Lonely Library / What's So Funny

episodes.synopsis: A little girl in Prince Edward Island is disappointed in her second hand bike/A little Mexican donkey refuses to eat corn.
episodes.title: Paint Job / Yummy In My Tummy

episodes.synopsis: A little boy has given up trying to learn to skate/A peacock and a flamingo living in India, argue over their pond.
episodes.title: Whiz Kid / Birds Of A Feather

episodes.synopsis: A dancer is too shy to perform on stage/A little Jamaican boy discovers his island through the lens of a camera.
episodes.title: Fancy Footwork / Say Jamaica

episodes.synopsis: Franny and a dragon learn that table manners may be a good idea after all. / Franny meets a frog who learns that sometimes a joke can go too far.
episodes.title: Franny's Manners / Swamp Thing

episodes.synopsis: Franny meets a girl who's not sure she has what it takes to be a "real" pirate. / Franny meets a young girl who's tending her family's flock of yaks.
episodes.title: A Pirate's Treasure / Nat the Yak

episodes.synopsis: Franny helps a little kangaroo realize that he can hop on his own. / Franny helps a fumbling clown overcome his reluctance to wear his glasses.
episodes.title: Hop To It / Make Them Laugh

episodes.synopsis: Franny helps a little bat overcome his fear of the dark. / Franny meets a polar bear who learns that swimming isn't so scary after all.
episodes.title: Night Time / Bear Facts

episodes.synopsis: Franny meets two elephants who learn that working together is better than competing. / Franny meets a crocodile who's reluctant to go to a party.
episodes.title: Jumbo Hi Jinx / The Fais Do Do
